snippet.title: Jet Kave Adventure - Teaser Trailer ESRB
snippet.description:
Watch the full reveal on July 11th, 2019.

Jet Kave Adventure brings everything you love about 2.5D platformers. Enjoy the skill-based action, challenging boss fights, clever secrets and thrilling set-pieces in a game where the Stone Age and Science-Fiction collide. Fly over pitfalls, smash through walls, knock out enemies and manipulate objects as you master the jet-fueled platforming to stop the alien threat once and for all.

Coming soon to Nintendo Switch™ and Nintendo Switch Lite™.
=================================
Official page: http://www.7lvls.com/jetkave/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/7lvls/
